default     deny  (rule-less components import nothing)
test_files  hybrid

components
  domain       whitelist
      internal/domain/**
      allow  std
  handler      whitelist
      internal/handler/**
      allow  domain, std
  main         whitelist
      cmd/**
      allow  *
  repository   whitelist
      internal/repository/**
      allow  domain, std, external
  service      whitelist
      internal/service/**
      allow  domain, std
